John C. PICKETT, Trustee In Bankruptcy of the Estate of Theodore F. Barnes, Bankrupt, v. LINCOLN JOINT STOCK LAND BANK. No. 1784. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Oct. 10, 1938. William Niklaus, of Lincoln, Neb., for appellant. C. A. Sorensen, of Lincoln, Neb., for appellee.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on motion of appellee, at appellant’s costs, for failure to prosecute.
